    "sourcePythonCode": "class Solution:\n    def moveZeroes(self, nums: List[int]) -> None:\n        k = 0\n        for i, x in enumerate(nums):\n            if x:\n                nums[k], nums[i] = nums[i], nums[k]\n                k += 1",
